Units exactly kya hote hai
Ans -px % vw vh em rem

1 - px kya hota hai - 1px on screen px me screen ka si size change nhi hote
2 % - jitna total hai uska hissa 70 % width dedo screen ko chota bada karenge toh yh bhi badelega
em -  em depend karta hai us element ke front size par, aur ye agar parent ko
dete hai to children par bhi apply hota hai
matalb kuch aisa:
consode kariye ek element hai jiske pass16px font size hai to 1em ki value 16px hogi 
aur font size change kiya to uske response mein em ki value bhi badhegi